```
 Sample Use Case:

You can test the analyzer with:

* Emails
* SMS messages
* Social media messages

Example:

```text
"Your account has been suspended. Click here to verify immediately."
```

 Limitations:

* Rule-based detection (not AI/ML-based)
* May produce false positives or miss advanced phishing attempts
* Requires manual input for analysis

